<PageLayout title={`${title} | Better Lives Building Tribes`} schema={schema} description="You moved to Colorado for good reasons. Maybe it was a job opportunity, a relationship, a fresh start, or simply the mountains calling. On paper, the decision made sense. You imagined adventure, new e">
